title: Quiz: How Well Do You Know Justin Timberlake?
text:
Celebrity Quiz: How Well Do You Know Justin Timberlake? In honor of JT's 36th birthday, take this quiz to find out how much you know about his music, movies, and his 50 other jobs. by Rebecah Jacobs 4h ago 
Today is pop star (and all around way-too-talented guy) Justin Timberlake ’s 36th birthday. He can do it all, from hosting Saturday Night Live to multi-platinum records, it’s hard to say what his occupation even is anymore. In honor of his birthday, we put together a quiz to see just how well you’ve kept up with all of JT’s many endeavors. See how well you fare in answering questions about everything Timberlake!
